Known Bugs
----------

  sound segfaults with some sound drivers. %-<

  matrox G200 : GL games don't display menus correctly (matrox GL bug ?)

  glh2mp:   The fire weapon for the Demoness in GL mode,
            draws lines across the screen.

  glhexen2: Eidolon doesn't jump down:  This is NOT a hexen2
	    engine issue, but is a HexenC (a.k.a. progs.dat)
	    issue. If you hit this bug, download a fix from
	    our site.

  glhexen2: The bosses seem too hard ???

